import React from 'react';
import { TextField } from '@material-ui/core';
import { FormDialog } from '../Shared/Dialog';

export const AddUserDialog = (props) =>
    <FormDialog isOpen={props.isOpen} onClose={props.onClose} title={props.title}>
      <TextField
      autoFocus
      required
      margin="dense"
      id="login"
      label="Login"
      type="text"
      fullWidth
      />

      <TextField
      autoFocus
      required
      margin="dense"
      id="password"
      label="Password"
      type="password"
      fullWidth
      />
    </FormDialog>

export const EditUserDialog = (props) =>
    <FormDialog isOpen={props.isOpen} onClose={props.onClose} title={props.title}>
      <TextField
            autoFocus
            required
            margin="dense"
            id="login"
            label="Login"
            type="text"
            fullWidth
          />

        <TextField
            autoFocus
            margin="dense"
            id="password"
            label="Password"
            type="password"
            fullWidth
          />

        <TextField
            autoFocus
            margin="dense"
            id="type"
            label="Type"
            type="password"
            fullWidth
          />
    </FormDialog>

export const DeleteUserDialog = (props) =>
    <FormDialog isOpen={props.isOpen} onClose={props.onClose} title={props.title}>
      <TextField
            autoFocus
            required
            margin="dense"
            id="login"
            label="Login"
            type="text"
            fullWidth
          />
    </FormDialog>
